node.text:
This ain’t your typical brunch 🤫 We throw it back with our 90s Themed Brunch 🎨 For 2 hours you get: bottomless top shelf drinks, art instruction & supplies to create your 90s masterpiece all while jamming to your favorite throwbacks! 

Also available our brunch menu with faves such as Chicken n Waffle Sliders & Shrimp n Grits. 🙌 Cop your tickets @ paintnpournyc.com
